mment picker work?</div><div style=\"font-size:14px;color:var(--text-secondary);line-height:1.6\">Paste your Instagram comments into the text area, configure your filters (remove duplicates, minimum word count), and click Pick Winner. The tool randomly selects a comment using a cryptographically secure random number generator.</div></div><div style=\"margin-bottom:12px;padding:20px;background:var(--bg-secondary);border-radius:var(--radius);border:1px solid var(--border)\"><div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:var(--text-primary);margin-bottom:8px\">Do I need to log in to Instagram?</div><div style=\"font-size:14px;color:var(--text-secondary);line-height:1.6\">No. Simply copy and paste the comments from your Instagram post. The tool works entirely in your browser with no API calls or logins required.</div></div><div style=\"margin-bottom:12px;padding:20px;background:var(--bg-secondary);border-radius:var(--radius);border:1px solid var(--border)\"><div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:var(--text-primary);margin-bottom:8px\">Is the selection truly random?</div><div style=\"font-size:14px;color:var(--text-secondary);line-height:1.6\">Yes. We use the Web Crypto API (crypto.getRandomValues) which provides cryptographically secure random numbers, ensuring a fair and unbiased selection.</div></div><div style=\"margin-bottom:12px;padding:20px;background:var(--bg-secondary);border-radius:var(--radius);border:1px solid var(--border)\"><div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:var(--text-primary);margin-bottom:8px\">Can I pick multiple winners?</div><div style=\"font-size:14px;color:var(--text-secondary);line-height:1.6\">Yes. Set the number of winners before picking, and the tool will select that many unique winners from the comment pool.</div></div></div><div style=\"margin-bottom:40px\"><h2 style=\"font-size:22px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:16px\">Related Tools</h2><div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px